  "statement": "The app MUST NOT alter a session it only meant to read.. Liveness and status remain side-effect-free probes (signal-0 existence check, no signals sent), exactly as today. Reading the board, a thread, the brain, a preview, or a diff MUST NOT resume or spawn a session \u2014 resume/spawn happens **only** on an explicit chat send. (See the existing `probeLiveness` discipline, ADR-005.)",
